name: Little Luke's Destiny
description:
Little Luke's Destiny

-Fully approved and certified by Lucasfilm 
-Giclee on Paper
-Edition Size: 150
-Size 13 x 19 paper dimension

The following features are exclusive to this store
-The print is hand signed and numbered
-FREE an original sketch of the character in a different pose.

Favourite characters from the Star Wars universe, mirroring key moments from their future, capturing the excitement, enthusiasm and hope that makes the Star Wars franchise so loved.

name: Sea Breeze
description:
A poster advertising Sea Breeze beer brewed in the fictional Rig City.

Exploring Rig City through the posters that adorn the walls, this image works as a one off piece as well as revealing information about where and when Rig City exists.

Gicleé Print on 308gsm Hahnemühle Photo Rag paper 
12" x 16" (paper dimension)
Ltd Ed 100
Signed
Hand Numbered

name: Steps, Leaps and Bounds
description:
Originally created to commemorate the life of astronaut and explorer Neil Armstrong, the first man to walk on another world. 

This illustration depicts the inspiration ignited by our tentative first steps in off world exploration.

Gicleé Print on 308gsm Hahnemühle Photo Rag paper 
12" x 16" (paper dimension)
Ltd Ed 150
Signed
Hand Numbered

name: Well, here we are
description:
